_sText:
Aim_47th_v2_remix by <|TTF|> Jackorito, released for Futura Studios (http://www.fpsbanana.com/studios/931)
-- 32 players, buyzones, no hidden weapons, bots supported, lag free --

This is a remake of aim_47th_v2 by 47th. It includes new areas and pathways, lighting, and features. Hope everyone likes it and have fun :P

Put in ...cstrike/maps

Known Issues:
There are a few cosmetic errors that involve water reflections and an error with the radar overviews. They Shouldn't cause lag or a game crash, so just ignore them. I may at somepoint re-upload the map with some of these fixed.

Special thanks to:
47th for making the original map.
The Makers Of: Pakrat, Vmex
Help and Suggestions - <|TTF|> Sexypanda, SGT-MESs, eVOL, crazypip666, <|tTf|> Pirate|Rancid
Beta Testing - <|TTF|> Sexypanda, SGT-MESs, eVOL, crazypip666
Helpful websites: VERC Collective, FPSBanana.com, VDC at Wikipedia, and Halfwit-2.com

This map is a release for Futura Studios. For more great maps, skins, and guis, upcomming releases or suggestions, goto the studios section of this site.

Thanks for downloading!!! Enjoy.
